{"tid":926883,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己總係同同事埋唔到堆","createTime":"2018-12-03T18:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T15:48:18.000Z","uid":205394,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1c4f0135171722f746b58871bd23ce107f8f6859","tid":926883,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T18:52:54.000Z","msg":"我之前間公司規模算少時入左職<br />\n當時公司只有一個大圈子<br />\n做做下公司大左，請多左人<br />\n分左圈子都好，我都算好多圈子都有份<br />\n走左重有好多都keep住聯絡<br />\n約出黎食下飯咁<br />\n<br />\n然後去到新公司<br />\n入面本身已經好多圈子（因為人多）<br />\n食飯時睇到一批批咁<br />\n佢地都好少話會主動接觸我<br />\n我又唔知佢地d底細，唔知點突入<br />\n加上唔係話特別世界仔類型<br />\n所以遲遲未埋到堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n回想舊公司有個新人話入黎時好唔開心<br />\n無人採佢無人理佢，自己又唔敢埋堆<br />\n好彩後黎跟左我，漸漸開始先埋到堆<br />\n而家到我面臨佢既問題了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a635e7af743b79df46d6842de52d02b4ee16076a","tid":926883,"uid":127864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T23:56:12.000Z","msg":"用李添命既思路藝術<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b622ef4363a5b0808f365ffd4d94b8adccaab848","tid":926883,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:08:43.000Z","msg":"唔埋堆仲好la,食完飯訓教<br />\n收工又準時<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c287f06c176831a794382fd84121b7e82bb31af1","tid":926883,"uid":133977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a635e7af743b79df46d6842de52d02b4ee16076a","tid":926883,"uid":127864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T23:56:12.000Z","msg":"用李添命既思路藝術<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:41:45.000Z","msg":"如果佢同你講皆大歡喜d劇情呢"},{"pid":"ff96991ea035b666380f2b32175bf4dc8a1d241a","tid":926883,"uid":191919,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:11:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03b05bc76a6985adc1e5c25419df164601f1d23b","tid":92